Huh?

Oh, sorry. Thought you said something. Keep hearing things lately.

Anyway, you've got some Tenebrara {@LinkCreature:35#20#overseers}, {@LinkCreature:35#18#destroyers}, and {@LinkCreature:35#17#dreadweavers} to take care of. Try not to...what?

Oh...sorry, something else again. Anyway, try not to have too much fun.

Talk to...talk to Tesran in Wyrmgorge when you've finished.
You're here for a reward? For not completing your mission? Try again.
